    public class GenericUpperLayerHandleIdPushOperation
extends SimpleHandleIdPushOperation
    This implementation of the PushOperation retrieves a foreign module specified by a generic upper layer parameter set as defined by the PduR. The relation between own and foreign elements is determined by referring to the same global pdu element residing in another module (E.g. EcuC) configuration container. This operation supports the following extension-point parameters:
    • moduleId: The id of the module for which to generated handle-ids
    • listPath: Schema-Path to the list with the handle-ids
    • idPath: Path relative to each list entry where the id variable can be found
    • pduRefPath: Path relative to each list entry where the reference to the global pdu can be found
    Input to this PushOperation is a HandleIdEvent.
